{"tid":39684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勉強遮住屁股！　日本天馬航空要空姐穿超短迷你裙挨轟","createTime":"2016-12-14T17:15:33.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T19:17:34.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ffbc8521329b0dd4e26f1a4cbcf62fec08515e7a","tid":39684,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T17:15:33.000Z","msg":"日本廉價航空天馬航空（Skymark Airlines）讓自家空姐穿上僅勉強遮住臀部的超短迷你裙，引起關注，但也被認為容易引發性騷擾。日本空服員聯盟（Japan Federation of Cabin Attendants）近日批航空公司，「我們擔心這樣的制服恐造成性騷擾等問題。」 <br />\n日本廉航「天馬航空」2013年宣布，從2014年3月起將引進新型空中巴士A330機種，隨著機型汰換，旗下空姐制服也換新裝，寶藍色的合身制服搭配同色系迷你裙、繫上黃絲巾，將洋溢親切笑容的空姐襯托得更加賞心悅目。天馬航空社長西久保慎一表示，為了強調「年輕化」，在A330客機上服務的空姐平均年齡均為20歲左右。"},{"pid":"7dc671aaa631adec84b1609cfdbd54ff506d5ee7","tid":39684,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T17:16:27.000Z","msg":"圖？"},{"pid":"3b0480b4b9edd9e44a1f4fa39844739b91d1fed2","tid":39684,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T17:18:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2014-03/28/10790014228148400632_11n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.xinhuanet.com%2Fworld%2F2014-03%2F28%2F10790014228148400632_11n.jpg&h=abc55272&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f760a59134bb29fc9bf269a018e332267c29a75e","tid":39684,"uid":50165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T17:20:10.000Z","msg":"呢啲咪識做生意囉"},{"pid":"0c295b220322993f6072c382ca56878bffd3383d","tid":39684,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T17:20:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2014-03/28/10790014228148400632_11n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.xinhuanet.com%2Fworld%2F2014-03%2F28%2F10790014228148400632_11n.jpg&h=abc55272&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n條裙咁撚長點搭你地d飛機呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99357d4e7be92dbd14c58d78b22bd3deccdd